beer.beer_description:
Throw on your jandals and chuck a few in the chilly bin. This is a tribute to our neighbours across the ditch. Using only cold-side NZ hops, we’ve loaded this brew to the brim with a huge double dry-hop of Nelson Sauvin & Riwaka. 
We’ve extracted all the citrusy, juicy goodness you can get from this succulent duo. Flock to it, this beer is choice as!
